  <synonym_of_species_name>Troximon alpestre A. Gray, Proc. Amer. Acad. Arts 19: 70. 1883; Agoseris alpestris (A. Gray) Greene; Microseris alpestris (A. Gray) Q. Jones ex Cronquist</synonym_of_species_name>
